txt.en: 'Mind ye, he died to protect us, the women of Byre Tor!'
'It's our duty to see his grandchild born safely into this world....'
'...no matter what our petty squabbles be with that girl!'
'We will patch you up, Thane. Try not to speak....'
'Ránmald, where... where are you, my child?'
'I am here, dear one! I have not left your side.'
'Ye cannot make us like her, no matter how many furs ye pile on us.'
'The Thane's family pampered her enough. Now she must learn to fend for herself!'
'We Byre Tor women can handle ourselves! So must she.'
'Strangers to Byre Tor think themselves better than us, but we always survive.'
'Hmf. Why did ye want to talk to us out here?'
'Take as much time as you need, my friend.'
'I know why the outsider brought us here....'
'Ye all heard Thane Aldstan's dying wish.'
